itemDisplayName: Deploy a Standard SKU Service Fabric managed cluster with existing load balancer
description: This template takes a minimum set of parameters and deploys a Standard SKU Service Fabric managed cluster with 2 node types. Node type 2 is configured to use existing load balancer.
